      "acceptanceCriteria": "Software version control, documented test suite, and configuration management records must be in place for the CFD solver and post-processing scripts.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023 R1) is under formal version control. A documented regression test suite covering benchmark cases has been executed and archived. Configuration management records are maintained for all simulation scripts. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
