      "acceptanceCriteria": "Code verification activities must demonstrate that the solver correctly implements the governing equations through benchmark or manufactured-solution tests.",
      "rationale": "The solver has been verified against the ASME V&V 20 lid-driven cavity benchmark and a Poiseuille flow manufactured solution. Observed convergence rates are consistent with the nominal second-order spatial accuracy of the discretisation scheme. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
