      "acceptanceCriteria": "A formal mesh convergence study using at least three systematically refined grids must be completed, with GCI reported for the primary QoI (hemolysis index).",
      "rationale": "Three hexahedral meshes (2.1 M, 5.8 M, 14.2 M cells) were used. GCI for the scalar stress-based hemolysis index at the worst-case operating point is 3.1%, within the 5% threshold. The medium mesh (5.8 M) was selected for production runs. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
