      "rationale": "Solver residuals for continuity and momentum drop six orders of magnitude in all production runs. Iterative convergence is confirmed by monitoring hemolysis index stabilisation over the final 500 iterations. Formal round-off or iterative error quantification is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
