      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2 a qualitative justification for the selected turbulence and hemolysis sub-models is sufficient; sensitivity analysis across alternative model forms is not required.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-ω turbulence model and Giersiepen–Wurzinger hemolysis power-law are standard choices for intravascular CFD at these Reynolds numbers and are consistent with FDA guidance. Qualitative justification is documented. Formal model-form uncertainty quantification is not required at MRL 2."
    },
